Narrow band of freezing rain hits southern Maine

The freezing rain accumulation has been enough to warrant extra attention on the road.

![](https://media.newscentermaine.com/assets/NCM/images/d16144a4-1599-46e6-b95a-8b101c75e52c/20260106T104253/d16144a4-1599-46e6-b95a-8b101c75e52c_16x9.jpg) ![](https://media.newscentermaine.com/assets/NCM/images/d16144a4-1599-46e6-b95a-8b101c75e52c/20260106T104253/d16144a4-1599-46e6-b95a-8b101c75e52c_750x422.jpg)

